message:
@PopeJamal Here's my thoughts. Use a statically generated site for our 'official' news feed and a bunch of screenshots and engine info on the main cubecreate.com site.

Then on the wiki we can have our community feeds and everything else there.

Furthermore, we can use sphinx to package official documentation with the engine. That'll also allow it to be printed into a manual form or something like that for distribution purposes.
